The paper discusses a compilation technique for model-based development of embedded systems, which is a topic that falls under software engineering (cs.SE). The technique involves converting hierarchical state machines into modular Horn clauses, which relates to programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also mentions safety analysis, which is a topic in formal methods (cs.FL) and embedded systems (cs.ET).
